snippet.title: Day Eleven: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard arrive at the High Court
snippet.description:
Cocaine-crazed Johnny Depp threatened to break the wrist of Amber Heard's female friend because they were "flirting" - before trashing a caravan and ripping off his wife's dress in frantic search for drugs'
Amber Heard is set to begin the second day of her evidence in Johnny Depp's libel case against The Sun over allegations of domestic violence. The Aquaman actress, 34, claims she feared Mr Depp, 57, was 'going to...
